  "text": "This paper is organized as follows. In Section 2, we introduce some notations and definitions and state some preliminary results which are needed in later sections. In Section 3, we establish some sufficient conditions for the existence of weighted pseudo-almost periodic solutions of [CITATION_1] . In Section 4, we prove that the weighted pseudo-almost periodic solution is globally exponentially stable. In Section 5, we give an example to illustrate the feasibility of our results obtained in previous sections.",
